<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 04:11:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>利库德集团内部人士认为，“不稳定”的本格维尔不太可能推翻内塔尼亚胡瘫痪的政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/unstable-ben-gvir-unlikely-to-bring-down-netanyahus-government-likud-insiders-believe/00000190-99a7-d3c0-a7b0-f9e75f200000</link><description>以色列极右翼国家安全部长似乎认为选举迫在眉睫，尽管他的行为鲁莽，但他的反对策略在民意调查中为他带来了良好的结果</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 03:00:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/unstable-ben-gvir-unlikely-to-bring-down-netanyahus-government-likud-insiders-believe/00000190-99a7-d3c0-a7b0-f9e75f200000</guid></item><item><title>士兵在加沙战斗中丧生；巴勒斯坦人报告至少 29 人在空袭中丧生后，以色列国防军展开调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-live/idf-investigating-after-palestinians-report-at-least-29-killed-in-gaza-airstrike/00000190-9a67-d71d-abb7-daf7f5800000</link><description>巴勒斯坦人报告称，加沙汗尤尼斯附近的学校大院遭到袭击，造成至少 29 人死亡、数十人受伤 ■ MDA 医疗服务：以色列北部戈兰地区的车辆被火箭直接击中，造成两人死亡 ■ 以色列国防军称拦截了两架从黎巴嫩越境进入以色列的无人机 ■叙利亚军队报告以色列袭击了叙利亚北部与伊朗有关的目标，没有人员伤亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 02:21:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article-live/idf-investigating-after-palestinians-report-at-least-29-killed-in-gaza-airstrike/00000190-9a67-d71d-abb7-daf7f5800000</guid></item><item><title>以色列宣布将非法前哨基地合法化，宣布 Evyatar 建在国有土地上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-moves-to-legalize-illegal-outpost-declares-evyatar-is-built-on-state-owned-land/00000190-9970-d3c0-a7b0-f97067cf0000</link><description>该决定是在安全内阁批准包括 Evyatar 在内的五个非法前哨基地合法化两周后做出的。声称拥有相关土地的巴勒斯坦人现在可以向最高法院质疑这一决定</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 22:04:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-moves-to-legalize-illegal-outpost-declares-evyatar-is-built-on-state-owned-land/00000190-9970-d3c0-a7b0-f97067cf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军事调查发现 10 月 7 日贝埃里战役期间部队行为存在严重缺陷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-finds-serious-flaws-in-troops-conduct-during-beeri-battles-on-october-7/00000190-9965-d3c0-a7b0-f96587ec0000</link><description>调查结果将于周四公布，熟悉调查结果的消息人士表示，调查还将重点关注一名高级指挥官炮击一处关押着 13 名人质的房屋的决定</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 21:37:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-finds-serious-flaws-in-troops-conduct-during-beeri-battles-on-october-7/00000190-9965-d3c0-a7b0-f96587ec0000</guid></item><item><title>第一次战斗六个月后，以色列军队返回舒贾耶：“不能保证这是最后一次”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/six-months-after-the-first-battle-israeli-forces-return-to-shujaiyeh/00000190-9885-d591-a7ff-fef7f23c0000</link><description>伞兵被告知，他们被部署执行 72 小时的行动，最终在加沙停留了两个月。在与国土报的对话中，其中一人承认目睹大规模人口流动是最具挑战性的：“它提醒我们，我们是人类”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 21:26:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/six-months-after-the-first-battle-israeli-forces-return-to-shujaiyeh/00000190-9885-d591-a7ff-fef7f23c0000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德负责人前往卡塔尔参加“决定性”加沙峰会；官员警告以色列和哈马斯之间仍存在巨大分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/mossad-chief-heads-to-decisive-gaza-summit-in-qatar-officials-warn-wide-gaps-remain/00000190-9907-d591-a7ff-fff7a9370000</link><description>以色列间谍头子将与中央情报局局长、卡塔尔总理和埃及情报部门负责人会面。以色列高级官员表示，如果内塔尼亚胡和辛瓦尔都没有破坏谈判，最终协议可能会导致以色列联盟的崩溃</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 20:29:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/mossad-chief-heads-to-decisive-gaza-summit-in-qatar-officials-warn-wide-gaps-remain/00000190-9907-d591-a7ff-fff7a9370000</guid></item><item><title>战争九个月后，内塔尼亚胡鲁莽的部长们忙着争吵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-09/ty-article/.highlight/nine-months-into-the-war-netanyahus-reckless-ministers-are-busy-bickering/00000190-9815-d590-affd-ba1599520000</link><description>对于所有反对内塔尼亚胡糟糕的极右翼联盟的人来说，在整个联盟面临崩溃之际，看着他的部长们在校园里公开互相辱骂，几乎可以让人感到放松。但是，当你知道无论谁赢了，我们都会输的时候，你很难对一场战斗感到兴奋。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 20:08:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-09/ty-article/.highlight/nine-months-into-the-war-netanyahus-reckless-ministers-are-busy-bickering/00000190-9815-d590-affd-ba1599520000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡因战争而试图推迟听证会，将于 12 月在腐败审判中作证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-testify-in-corruption-trial-in-december-after-an-attempt-to-delay-due-to-war/00000190-98d3-d590-affd-bad7c5840000</link><description>由于加沙战争和案件范围，内塔尼亚胡的律师要求推迟到2025年3月开始辩护证词。然而，法官强调公众利益需要迅速推进</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 19:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-testify-in-corruption-trial-in-december-after-an-attempt-to-delay-due-to-war/00000190-98d3-d590-affd-bad7c5840000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长批准以色列国防军计划下个月向极端正统派人士发送征兵通知</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/defense-chief-approves-idf-plan-to-send-draft-notices-to-ultra-orthodox-men-next-month/00000190-9865-d590-affd-ba755fed0000</link><description>国防部的声明没有具体说明将发送多少份征兵通知，但军方消息人士称将发送数千份。以色列国防军副参谋长表示，军队今年希望征召 4,800 名正统派男子，明年也将征召同样数量的士兵</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 18:47:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/defense-chief-approves-idf-plan-to-send-draft-notices-to-ultra-orthodox-men-next-month/00000190-9865-d590-affd-ba755fed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列戈兰高地遭火箭弹袭击，造成两人死亡；真主党声称对此次袭击负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/two-killed-in-rocket-strike-on-golan-heights-hezbollah-claims-responsibility-for-barrage/00000190-988a-d591-a7ff-fefa72c20000</link><description>大约 40 枚火箭弹射向戈兰高地，其中一枚击中了两人驾驶的汽车；该地区多处地点发生火灾；真主党表示，此次袭击是为了回应以色列在叙利亚针对一名关键特工的袭击事件</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 18:22:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/two-killed-in-rocket-strike-on-golan-heights-hezbollah-claims-responsibility-for-barrage/00000190-988a-d591-a7ff-fefa72c20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院命令贝都因家庭向国家支付超过一百万谢克尔以支付驱逐费用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-orders-bedouin-family-to-pay-state-over-a-million-shekels-in-eviction-costs/00000190-978d-dfc0-a3f3-bffd333f0000</link><description>贝尔谢巴地方法院裁定，拒绝该州驱逐条款的四名贝都因家庭成员必须支付驱逐费用。他们辩称，国家不允许他们自行拆除房屋，而且规定的金额过高</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 17:58:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-orders-bedouin-family-to-pay-state-over-a-million-shekels-in-eviction-costs/00000190-978d-dfc0-a3f3-bffd333f0000</guid></item><item><title>前以色列国防军发言人谈内塔尼亚胡及其政府如何落入哈马斯手中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-and-many-other-reservists-did-not-enlist-to-carry-out-a-nakba/00000190-916b-d0cb-abb9-f77b0e570000</link><description>八个月来，前以色列国防军国际媒体发言人彼得·勒纳（Peter Lerner）从一个工作室到另一个工作室，试图让全世界相信以色列国防军在加沙行动的合法性。现在他说：“在国际舞台上，内塔尼亚胡和他的政府带领以色列失败了”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 17:10:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-and-many-other-reservists-did-not-enlist-to-carry-out-a-nakba/00000190-916b-d0cb-abb9-f77b0e570000</guid></item><item><title>根据修订后的仇恨言论政策，Meta 将禁止针对“犹太复国主义者”的“非人化”帖子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/meta-to-ban-posts-targeting-zionists-with-dehumanizing-comparisons-to-jews-israelis/00000190-9854-d0d3-a5f3-98fc06bd0000</link><description>此举标志着这家科技巨头态度的转变，此前该公司认为“犹太复国主义者”一词仅在非常明确的情况下才代表犹太人。他们的声明中写道：“我们将删除使用反犹太主义刻板印象或威胁伤害的内容”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 17:03:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/meta-to-ban-posts-targeting-zionists-with-dehumanizing-comparisons-to-jews-israelis/00000190-9854-d0d3-a5f3-98fc06bd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 277 天：红新月会表示其加沙城所有设施均已关闭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-277-red-crescent-says-all-its-gaza-city-facilities-have-shut-down/00000190-9835-d590-affd-ba35f9d80000</link><description>以色列人质丹妮拉·吉尔博亚 (Daniela Gilboa) 的家人批准出版哈马斯一月份发布的她被囚禁的视频 ■ 新一轮停战谈判定于周三在多哈举行 ■ 真主党发布以色列北部以色列国防军基地和军事基础设施的照片 ■ 据报道以色列杀人真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉的前保镖在贝鲁特至大马士革公路上罢工 ■ 战争进入 277 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 16:40:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-277-red-crescent-says-all-its-gaza-city-facilities-have-shut-down/00000190-9835-d590-affd-ba35f9d80000</guid></item><item><title>“不可接受”：马克龙在与内塔尼亚胡的通话中指责以色列部长干涉法国大选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-07-09/ty-article/macron-slams-israeli-ministers-interference-in-french-election-in-call-with-netanyahu/00000190-980a-d044-a997-d81e1f510000</link><description>选举前几天，马克龙警告内塔尼亚胡，侨民部长阿米猜·奇克利公开支持马琳·勒庞的极右翼国家集会党，构成对法国内政的不当干涉。以色列外交官称奇克利损害了与法国的关系</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:25:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-07-09/ty-article/macron-slams-israeli-ministers-interference-in-french-election-in-call-with-netanyahu/00000190-980a-d044-a997-d81e1f510000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡联盟裂痕加深，利库德集团谴责本格维尔“不负责任的行为”并撤回议会法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/likud-blasts-ben-gvirs-irresponsible-behavior-pulls-bills-as-coalition-rift-deepens/00000190-97d5-d590-affd-b7d551470000</link><description>联合党鞭子奥菲尔·卡茨(Ofir Katz)表示，“我希望联合党帮助反对派伤害我们的情况能够停止。”他援引奥兹玛·耶胡迪特(Otzma Yehudit)的行为和主席本·格维尔(Ben-Gvir)拒绝支持部长级委员会批准的沙斯法案作为撤回所有计划的理由。议程上的法案</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:05:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/likud-blasts-ben-gvirs-irresponsible-behavior-pulls-bills-as-coalition-rift-deepens/00000190-97d5-d590-affd-b7d551470000</guid></item><item><title>比比如何滥用以色列预算来保住权力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/how-bibi-is-misusing-israels-budget-to-cling-to-power/00000190-97c4-d590-affd-b7d456e50000</link><description>由于担心所需的支出削减和增税可能会导致政府垮台，2025 年支出计划的进展陷入停滞</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 14:08:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/how-bibi-is-misusing-israels-budget-to-cling-to-power/00000190-97c4-d590-affd-b7d456e50000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日哈马斯入侵加沙附近的以色列海滩将自战争开始以来首次开放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/destroyed-israeli-beach-near-gaza-border-set-to-open-for-first-time-since-war-began/00000190-976d-d8d3-adb9-dfff48100000</link><description>加沙地带北部的齐金海滩是10月7日以色列国防军与哈马斯恐怖分子之间激烈战斗的地点，这场战斗造成11名平民和1名士兵死亡。它已焕然一新，将于八月重新向公众开放</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 13:34:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/destroyed-israeli-beach-near-gaza-border-set-to-open-for-first-time-since-war-began/00000190-976d-d8d3-adb9-dfff48100000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦权力机构首次向以色列法院提交请愿书，希望推翻恐怖受害者赔偿法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/in-first-ever-petition-to-israeli-court-pa-looks-to-reverse-terror-victim-damages-laws/00000190-96ef-d8d3-adb9-deff2a800000</link><description>议会三月份颁布的法律允许恐怖袭击受害者及其家人向巴勒斯坦权力机构提起损害赔偿诉讼，但请愿书声称这些法律“违宪”，并将导致巴勒斯坦权力机构“经济崩溃”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 11:53:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/in-first-ever-petition-to-israeli-court-pa-looks-to-reverse-terror-victim-damages-laws/00000190-96ef-d8d3-adb9-deff2a800000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯10月7日袭击以色列7名加沙人，他们的命运不明</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-attacked-7-gazans-in-israel-on-october-7-their-fates-are-unknown/00000190-9684-dae0-a59d-96bc94d60000</link><description>在一张照片中，10 月 7 日遭到袭击的货车内有尸体。在另一张照片中，哈马斯恐怖分子从车里活捉了两人。除了尸体被送回家人身边的司机之外，九个月以来，以色列没有人知道其他加沙乘客的遭遇，直到上周</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 11:08:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-attacked-7-gazans-in-israel-on-october-7-their-fates-are-unknown/00000190-9684-dae0-a59d-96bc94d60000</guid></item></channel></rss>